<%= erb :header_file %>
<div class="jumbotron">
  <div class="container" style="padding: 40px 15px;text-align: center;">
    <h1>Rules</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h2>Be Excellent To Each Other</h2>
      <p>Don't grief, don't spam the chat, do be cool, etc.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h2>Invitation Only</h2>
      <p>This server uses a whitelist, meaning you must be accepted onto the server
      to play. When you sign up for the startup service, ensure that you are using
      your minecraft username, otherwise you may not be able to actually get on the
      server.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h2>Hardcore Mode Only</h2>
      <p>This server uses a modified form of Hardcore mode. When you die, you will be
      banned from the server for about five minutes. Every time you die, that amount
      of time doubles. So die twice and you'll be banned ten minutes, thrice and
      twenty minutes, etc.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12">
      <h2>Questions? Concerns?</h2>
      <p>Reach out to me directly or email me at alafleurminecraft@gmail.com</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%= erb :footer_file %>